[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第十",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚卿",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "光梵大師賜紫沙門臣惟淨等",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "奉　詔譯「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，即如大海。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a07_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、為大寶聚；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、深難徹底；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a08_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、廣大無量；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、次第漸深；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不宿死屍；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a09_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、皆同一味；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、容受眾流；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a10_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、潮不失時；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、水族所依；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、無有邊際。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a11_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是菩薩為大寶聚？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海廣積眾寶，閻浮提中一切人眾，咸取其寶無有窮盡，菩薩亦復如是，廣積一切智功德寶，一切有情皆取是寶亦無窮盡，是即菩薩為大寶聚。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海深難徹底，菩薩亦復如是，一切有情於菩薩法莫測其際。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海廣大無量，菩薩亦復如是，功德智慧廣大無量。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海次第漸深，菩薩亦復如是，一切智深、一切智漸深、一切智極深。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海不宿死屍。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a21_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大海法爾如是故，菩薩亦復如是，不與煩惱結漏及不善知識而所共止。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩法爾如是故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海眾流入中皆同一味，所謂鹹味，菩薩亦復如是，積集一切善法皆同一味，所謂一切智味。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a26_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海容受眾流，而其海水不增不減，菩薩亦復如是，容受無量一切法水，而菩薩智慧不增不減。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海潮不失時，菩薩亦復如是，所應成熟化度有情亦不過時。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海為諸水族依止窟宅，菩薩亦復如是，為一切有情一切善法之所依止。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大海一切有情悉取其水而無邊際，菩薩亦復如是，廣為一切有情宣說法要，亦無邊際。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者即如大海。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者得微妙智。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、善求出離；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b08_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、善知諸出離法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、善知諸法平等；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、善知諸法如幻；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、善知一切法相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、善解甚深難測緣生之法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b11_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、善知業不思議；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、善知諸所說義；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、善了如實義；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b12_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者善觀真實智。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是菩薩善求出離，乃至善觀真實智？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂若菩薩作是思惟：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我應觀察諸世間相。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』觀見世間貪火熾然瞋煙蓬㶿，癡暗覆蔽瞑然無託，菩薩乃起是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『此諸有情，云何能得出離？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』菩薩即為勤求出離及出離法，由得出離法故，即能隨知諸法平等。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由知諸法平等故，即能如實知諸法如幻。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由知諸法如幻故，即如實知一切法相。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由知法相故，即能思察甚深難測緣生之法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由能思察緣生法故，即能解了業不思議。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故，菩薩雖知世間諸法無實，而亦顯示種種業報，由是之故得微妙智，能於諸佛菩薩所說義中而悉了知，由了知故即能開解如實之義。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "解如實義故，即能觀真實智，見真實故，能度有情出離生死。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得微妙智。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得隨應辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、開示諸法無我；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、無有情；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、無壽命；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、無養育；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、無補特伽羅；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、無作者；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、無受者；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、無知者；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、無見者；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、顯示一切法空都無主宰，皆是虛妄不實分別，諸法但從緣生故有。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若得一切法無我相應，彼即隨順法性，由是之故，於一切法無有情、無壽命、無養育、無補特伽羅、無作者、無受者、無知者、無見者等，如理相應即能隨順法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是之故，了知一切法空都無主宰，皆是虛妄不實分別，諸法但從緣生故有，如理相應即能隨順法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若隨順法性故，即於法性不相違背，不違背故乃能正說諸法，正說法故善入法性，入法性故乃能開示彼一切法，開示法故彼之辯才乃名隨應。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得隨應辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得樂說辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c16_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、辯才無著；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、無盡；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、相續；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、不畏大眾；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不卑下；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、無恐怖；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c18_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、不共；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、不輕慢；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、無邊；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、無礙解。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得樂說辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得清淨辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、無有謇吃；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、詞無雜亂；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、遠離卑劣；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、語不高戾；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、義無減失；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、文無缺漏；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、聲無短闕；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、無不知時；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、言無麁獷；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、無不明了。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c25_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩者，所有辯才無有謇吃。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於大眾中無怯弱故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才而無雜亂。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩智慧安然無畏。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才而無卑劣。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0729c29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩處大眾中，猶如師子離諸恐懼。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才語不高戾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已離煩惱故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有煩惱語即高戾，無即不爾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才義無減失。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已得法故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不得法即於義中有所減失，得即不爾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才文無缺漏。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "廣解諸論故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若解論尠少即文有缺漏，廣解即不爾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才聲無短闕。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩妙解一切音聲故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不解者即於音聲有所短闕，解即不爾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才無不知時，所應前說而不後說，若應後說亦不前說。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩善知諸時分故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才言無麁獷，無不悅意，無不樂聽。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已能遠離語過失故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有語過失者，言即麁獷，無即不爾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，所有辯才無不明了。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a15_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩根性利故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若鈍根者即不明了，利即不爾。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得清淨辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得一切有情歡喜辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、愛語；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、熙怡面相遠離顰蹙；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、如義語；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、如法語；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、平等語；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、不自高；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、不輕他；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、無染著；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、無觸惱；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、具種種辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩能以愛語令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，常現熙怡善相遠離顰蹙，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，常出如義語及美妙語，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，常出法語及利益語，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，常為有情平等說法，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730a28_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，而不自高，遠離驕慢高舉之咎，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，不輕於他，常為有情恭敬說法，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，離諸染著具淨尸羅，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，離諸觸惱具多忍力，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又菩薩者，具種種辯才常出悅意之語，令諸有情咸生歡喜。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得一切有情歡喜辯才。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，得信順說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、非法器有情菩薩不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者有障礙者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、有所得見者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、邪異外道不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不起樂欲心者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、不發清淨心者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、諂曲心者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、求活命者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、貪著利養慳嫉所纏者不為說法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、盲聾瘖瘂者不為說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不作法慳亦不祕法，於諸有情無不憐愍，為利有情而不棄背。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有有情非法器者，菩薩乃起是念：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『此等有情，而於如來法律之中起於捨行。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若然者，諸佛菩薩當為何等有情說法？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具信有情，諸佛菩薩當為說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若善根已成熟者，是法器者，於先佛所植眾德本者，無諂誑者，不詐現威儀者，不耽著利養者，深心具足者，為善知識所攝受者，具足善相人所樂見者，根性明利於所聞法中解其義者，隨所得法勤行精進者，如佛所說能修行者，此等有情，諸佛菩薩乃為說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即得信順說法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者為說法師。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、修集佛法故說法，不見有佛法可得，亦復不見有所修集；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、修集波羅蜜多故說法，不見波羅蜜多可得，亦復不見有所修集；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、修集菩薩法故說法，不見有菩薩法可得，亦復不見有所修集；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、斷煩惱故說法，不見有煩惱可得，亦不見斷；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、厭離離貪寂滅故說法，不見有厭離離貪寂滅可得；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、為得須陀洹、斯陀含、阿那含果故說法，不見有須陀洹、斯陀含、阿那含可得，亦不見果；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、為得阿羅漢果故說法，不見有阿羅漢可得，亦不見果；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、為得緣覺果故說法，不見有緣覺可得，亦不見果；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、斷我執取著故說法，不見有我可得，亦不見執著；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、顯示業報故說法，不見有業可得，亦不見報。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等一切法皆無實體，但以假名宣說，名亦無所有。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c16_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文字無自性，法離文字故，但以世俗虛假施設於無名中，是故建立諸法名字。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼名空，本虛假故，勝義諦中無虛假名。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無假名故，於勝義中無虛妄法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼虛妄法者，誑惑愚人故。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者即為說法師。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，能順觀法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、菩薩雖順觀法性而不壞色相，雖順觀法性不壞受想行識相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、雖順觀法性，不壞欲界相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、雖順觀法性，不壞色界相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、雖順觀法性，不壞無色界相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、雖順觀法性，不壞諸法相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、雖順觀法性，不見諸法隨順相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、雖順觀法性，不見有情相；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0730c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、雖順觀法性，亦不墮斷見；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、雖順觀法性，而不失正道；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、雖順觀法性，亦不離智慧方便。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修如是十種法者，即能順觀法性。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩若修十種法者，善解法界理。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、有慧；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、為善知識攝受；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a05_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、發起精進；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、離諸障染；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、善修淨行；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、尊重讚法；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、善修空觀；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、離有所得見；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、趣向正道；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、見真實法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩具智慧故，而能勤求諸善知識；",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見善知識已，心生歡喜，如師尊想，親近依止。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由能依止善知識故，即發起精進，斷除一切不善之法，圓滿一切清淨善法，勤行遠離一切障染，離障染故獲得輕安，善修淨行離身語心一切過失。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由清淨故於所得法尊重稱讚，由重法故多習空觀，習空觀故不起有所得見，離有所得見故順行正道，入正道故能觀真實。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何名真實？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a17_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如實之義，乃名真實。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何名如實？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不虛妄故，名為如實。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a19_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何名不虛妄？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所謂真如，無不真如、無異真如。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a21_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何名真如？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法唯內所證，非文字語言而能表示。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a23_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此法出過諸文字故，離諸言說故，超越一切語言境界，出於言道離諸戲論，離作非作無動無靜，離諸尋伺，是不思議境界。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無相非無相而悉遠離出諸相境，超諸凡境，出凡夫行，過諸魔境，超越一切煩惱境界。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離諸識境，安處無住最上寂靜聖智境界，是故此法唯內所證，是即無垢無染潔白清淨，最上最勝第一無比，常住堅固究竟無壞之法，如來出世若不出世，是法常住。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731b03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩為求此法，歷百千種難行苦行故得是法，得是法已，令諸有情悉住此法。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731b04_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731b05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故說此法名為真如，說名實際，說名一切智，說名一切種智，說名不思議界，說名不二界。",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731b07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說除蓋障菩薩所問經卷第十",
        "from": "T14n0489_010:0731b08_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]